00:01:08.650 --> 00:01:12.155
we&nbsp;could&nbsp;congratulate&nbsp;her
only&nbsp;on&nbsp;Facebook&nbsp;or&nbsp;Twitter…

00:01:12.776 --> 00:01:20.746
and&nbsp;wish&nbsp;her&nbsp;and&nbsp;Harry&nbsp;lots&nbsp;of&nbsp;peace,
health,&nbsp;happiness&nbsp;and&nbsp;so&nbsp;on…

