But&nbsp;those&nbsp;are&nbsp;our&nbsp;daily&nbsp;wishes!

00:01:22.479 --> 00:01:25.855
So&nbsp;why&nbsp;not&nbsp;get&nbsp;a&nbsp;bunch&nbsp;of&nbsp;cool&nbsp;people
togetherand make&nbsp;a&nbsp;video&nbsp;with&nbsp;those&nbsp;vows?

