And&nbsp;for&nbsp;showing&nbsp;us&nbsp;that&nbsp;“It&nbsp;is our
choices&nbsp;that show what&nbsp;we&nbsp;truly&nbsp;are,

00:02:59.301 --> 00:03:01.240
