00:03:09.891 --> 00:03:12.202
We&nbsp;wish&nbsp;the&nbsp;values&nbsp;taught&nbsp;in&nbsp;Harry&nbsp;Potter,

00:03:12.202 --> 00:03:17.233
of&nbsp;tolerance,&nbsp;love&nbsp;and&nbsp;so&nbsp;many&nbsp;others,
to&nbsp;be&nbsp;recalled&nbsp;everyday&nbsp;throughout&nbsp;the&nbsp;world.

00:03:17.233 --> 00:03:22.447
How&nbsp;funny:&nbsp;we&nbsp;recorded&nbsp;all&nbsp;this&nbsp;and&nbsp;ended
